summary: Hi, my name is Jasper van Zaanen and I am the founder of Cinematic Seconds. The Film Production Company in and around Leiden. With over 3 years of experience, Cinematic Seconds is specialised in making high quality custom films for companies and individuals. Whether your company needs a brand new commercial or explanatory video, Cinematic Seconds will guide you through the entire process. From idea, to planning, to shoot, to edit, to finally an end product. The craft ship has always been focussed on the customer, providing a unique set of imagery combined with high quality music, sound effects and colour grades.
